<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/57099123-raphi"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1466790573i/57099123._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/57099123-raphi">Raphi</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes, most definitely! Everything about it is gorgeous, and the storytelling is simply magnificent. There&apos;s also the added bonus that it will take you <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes, most definitely! Everything about it is gorgeous, and the storytelling is simply magnificent. There's also the added bonus that it will take you as long as you want it to to finish it, since it consists simply of pictures, though I do advise that you take your time with it and go through it slowly to get the most out of the images.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
