        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1644828728" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8517155632639605279">This is a wondrous and wonderful book. Entirely told in drawings &amp; pictures, not a word at all in the pages, apart from the title on the cover. My first &apos;graphic novel&apos;. Beautifully designed &apos;in sepia&apos;, a weird and touching story. About a man who leaves his wife and little daughter to emigrate to a new country, to find work and earn a living. But it is no ordinary story, it is full of fantasy images, creatures and weird observations. It seems to be symbolic for people going to another country to</span>
  <span id="freeText8517155632639605279" style="display:none">This is a wondrous and wonderful book. Entirely told in drawings &amp; pictures, not a word at all in the pages, apart from the title on the cover. My first 'graphic novel'. Beautifully designed 'in sepia', a weird and touching story. About a man who leaves his wife and little daughter to emigrate to a new country, to find work and earn a living. But it is no ordinary story, it is full of fantasy images, creatures and weird observations. It seems to be symbolic for people going to another country to live, overcome by weird, scary but also beautiful new experiences. This is translated into a surrealistic, also scifi surrounding with the weirdest animals, shapes and creatures, scary experiences and wonderful encounters. A special book....highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8517155632639605279" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

