</a><br><br>It managed to capture solitude, wistfulness, and hopefulness in a little over 100 pages, and it was magical.<br><br><i>*Note: I'm an Amazon Affiliate. If you're interested in buying</i> <b>The Arrival</b>, <i>just click on the image below to go through my link. I'll make a small commission!*</i><br><a target="_blank" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0439895294/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=0439895294&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=natalie013-20&amp;linkId=5128d6ad19ed1dd36779a8d339b6a0ee" rel="nofollow noopener">
