<div id="review_985858930" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/985858930" />
    <a title="Jan Philipzig" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/32295170-jan-philipzig"><img alt="Jan Philipzig" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1412522099p2/32295170.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/985858930?book_show_action=true">Jul 04, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jan Philipzig" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jan Philipzig" href="/user/show/32295170-jan-philipzig">Jan Philipzig</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780439895293" href="/book/show/431274.The_Arrival">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=family">family</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=immigration">immigration</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=friendship">friendship</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=wordless">wordless</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=levine-books">levine-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32295170-jan-philipzig?shelf=australasian">australasian</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer985858930" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7978122633492082236"><b>Shaun Tan`s Universal Masterpiece</b><br/><br/>Shaun Tan&apos;s graphic novel <i>The Arrival</i> tells the story of the refugee experience, depicting its sense of deprivation, danger, loneliness, discovery, and wonder.<br/><br/>Rooted in the picture-story tradition that predates modern comics, the book&apos;s wordless language mirrors the protagonist&apos;s inability to communicate though words in his new environment; the surreal images provide the story with universal relevance.<br/><br/>Brilliantly conceived and masterfully realized, <i>The Arrival</i> is</span>
  <span id="freeText7978122633492082236" style="display:none"><b>Shaun Tan`s Universal Masterpiece</b><br /><br />Shaun Tan's graphic novel <i>The Arrival</i> tells the story of the refugee experience, depicting its sense of deprivation, danger, loneliness, discovery, and wonder.<br /><br />Rooted in the picture-story tradition that predates modern comics, the book's wordless language mirrors the protagonist's inability to communicate though words in his new environment; the surreal images provide the story with universal relevance.<br /><br />Brilliantly conceived and masterfully realized, <i>The Arrival</i> is the rare case of a graphic novel that can be recommended to just about anyone, regardless of age or cultural background.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="7978122633492082236" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

